ong strike length of some 2000 km. Citation: Yang, J., P. A. Cawood, and Y. Du (2010), Detrital record of mountain building: Provenance of Jurassic foreland basin to the Dabie Mountains, Tectonics, 29, TC4011, doi: 10.1029/2009TC002600.},
