icates that the assemblage process of the Yangtze with Cathaysia blocks might be episodic with the collisional time of the Eastern Jiangnan Orogen being significantly earlier than that of the Central Jiangnan Orogen. An early Neoproterozoic arc-continent assembly model is herein proposed for the Jiangnan Orogen. (C) 2015 Elsevier B.V. All rights reserved.},
